et - Expense Totals

USAGE:
    et [tax|tip|fees] [-a] [-c=category] [-g=group]

DESCRIPTION:
    Calculate expense totals and statistics. Can filter by category
    and group results by various criteria.

OPTIONS:
    tax
        Show tax totals only

    tip
        Show tip totals only

    fees
        Show fees totals only

    -a
        Search all expense files

    -c=category
        Filter by specific category

    -g=group
        Group results by:
        category     - Group by category
        description  - Group by description
        name         - Group by name
        year         - Group by year
        month        - Group by month
        day          - Group by day

EXAMPLES:
    et
    et tax
    et -c=groceries
    et -g=category
    et -a -g=month
